xperience", "group_key": "our", "sizes": [], "addons": [], "allergens": [], "park_area": "EPCOT"}], "Our Kaiseki Experience | Ichiju Sansai \u2013 A Modern Beginning": [{"date": "2026-01-21", "start_date": "2026-01-21", "end_date": "2026-06-01", "price": null, "description": "We start with ichiju sansai\u2014one soup, two dishes\u2014the foundation of Japanese cuisine. Inspired by the cha-kaiseki ritual of \u201cfour bowls,\u201d this course invites you to open each lidded bowl at once and experience the beginning of your meal with all five senses. Seasonal ingredients and careful preparation set the tone for what\u2019s to come.", "group": "Our Kaiseki Experience", "group_key": "our", "sizes": [], "addons": [], "allergens": [], "park_area": "EPCOT"}], "Our Kaiseki Experience | Main Course \u2013 Where East Meets West": [{"date": "2026-01-21", "start_date": "2026-01-21", "end_date": "2026-06-01", "price": null, "description": "Our main course brings together Japanese ingredients and French-inspired techniques. This is where tradition meets creativity\u2014where rich flavors, beautiful plating, and a touch of surprise come together in harmony.", "group": "Our Kaiseki Experience", "group_key": "our", "sizes": [], "addons": [], "allergens": [], "park_area": "EPCOT"}], "Our Kaiseki Experience | Matcha & Sweet \u2013 A Peaceful Finish": [{"date": "2026-01-21", "start_date": "2026-01-21", "end_date": "2026-06-01", "price": null, "description": "We end with a handcrafted seasonal dessert and freshly prepared matcha, made in front of you. The quiet ritual of tea, the sound of water, and the scent of matcha create a serene conclusion to your experience.", "group": "Our Kaiseki Experience", "group_key": "our", "sizes": [], "addons": [], "allergens": [], "park_area": "EPCOT"}], "Our Kaiseki Experience | Rice Dish \u2013 A Gentle Ending": [{"date": "2026-01-21", "start_date": "2026-01-21", "end_date": "2026-06-01", "price": null, "description": "The final savory course is a sim